      "seed": 239099003,
      "version": 713,
      "versionNonce": 1946173589,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1766015578031,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Layer 1:\n\n\nGrass fades into generic cave?\nMurky polluted toxic area?\nbasic fantasy creatures like goblins and rock golems?\nor is this game techy and futuristic. Maybe aliens down there? so basic robots that are rusty?\nnot dangerous, but should have some things in it that keep the player on edge, should be moderately difficult to find footing to traverse down. use of ropes and ladders and mining out stairways are important\nI know i want it to be grand and almost imposing. Most certainly will have some water in it",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Layer 1:\n\n\nGrass fades into generic cave?\nMurky polluted toxic area?\nbasic fantasy creatures like goblins and rock golems?\nor is this game techy and futuristic. Maybe aliens down there? so basic robots that are rusty?\nnot dangerous, but should have some things in it that keep the player on edge, should be moderately difficult to find footing to traverse down. use of ropes and ladders and mining out stairways are important\nI know i want it to be grand and almost imposing. Most certainly will have some water in it",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
