      "versionNonce": 735603802,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "16nBF_IxS7gmIpp9VBtbg",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1766393797533,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CHUNK UPDATES:\n\n1. make an array called dirty_chunks\n\n2. any time a block is updated using \"set_block\" (which will be every case):\n    - place block: set_block(loc, type)\n    - break block: set_block(loc, null or 0)\nif (!dirty):\n    dirty = true\n    dirty_chunks.append(chunk)\n\n3. add a loop to process for the dirty chunks:\n    while not dirty_chunks.is_empty():\n        var next_chunk = dirty_chunks.pop_front()\n        next_chunk.is_dirty = false\n        load_queue.push_front(next_chunk.position)\n        \n4. these go through the exact same process as loading (hopefully c# is fast enough for this)\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "CHUNK UPDATES:\n\n1. make an array called dirty_chunks\n\n2. any time a block is updated using \"set_block\" (which will be every case):\n    - place block: set_block(loc, type)\n    - break block: set_block(loc, null or 0)\nif (!dirty):\n    dirty = true\n    dirty_chunks.append(chunk)\n\n3. add a loop to process for the dirty chunks:\n    while not dirty_chunks.is_empty():\n        var next_chunk = dirty_chunks.pop_front()\n        next_chunk.is_dirty = false\n        load_queue.push_front(next_chunk.position)\n        \n4. these go through the exact same process as loading (hopefully c# is fast enough for this)\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
